<html><head><style>body{font-family:'Segoe UI', Calibri, sans-serif; line-height:1.6;} h1{color:#2E4053; border-bottom:2px solid #2E4053;} h2{color:#2874A6;} code{background:#F4F6F6; padding:2px; font-family:Consolas, monospace;}</style></head><body><h1>HTML Template: attendance.html</h1>
<h2>1. Executive Summary</h2>
<p>Defines the structural layout and content for a specific web page view.</p>
<h2>2. Code Logic &amp; Functionality</h2>
<p>Uses the Jinja2 templating engine. The file allows for dynamic data insertion using <code>{{ variable }}</code> syntax and control structures like <code>{% if %}</code> loops within standard HTML markup.</p>
<h2>3. Key Concepts &amp; Definitions</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Jinja2</strong>: A modern and designer-friendly templating language for Python.</li>
<li><strong>Template Inheritance</strong>: The ability to extend a base layout (<code>base.html</code>) to avoid code duplication.</li>
<li><strong>DOM</strong>: Document Object Model, the data representation of the objects that comprise the structure and content of a document on the web.</li>
</ul>
<h2>4. Location Details</h2>
<p><strong>Path</strong>: <code>templates\tutor\attendance.html</code>
<strong>Type</strong>: .HTML File</p>
<h2>5. Source Code Preview (Snippet)</h2>
<p>Running typical software analysis on this file:</p>
<p>```html
{% extends "base.html" %}</p>
<p>{% block title %}Take Attendance - {{ activity.name }}{% endblock %}</p>
<p>{% block content %}</p>
<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-10">
            <div class="mb-4">
                <a href="{{ url_for('tutor_dashboard') }}" class="text-decoration-none text-muted mb-2 d-inline-block">
                    <i class="fas fa-arrow-left me-1"></i> Back to Dashboard
                </a>
                <h2 class="text-primary mb-0">Attendance: {{ activity.name }}</h2>
                <p class="text-muted">{{ activity.day_of_week }} | {{ activity.start_time }} - {{ activity.end_time }}
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="card shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white p-4">
                    <div class="row align-items-center">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <h5 class="mb-0"><i class="fas fa-clipboard-check me-2"></i>Mark Attendance</h5>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <div class="input-group">
                                <span class="input-group-text bg-white"><i class="fas fa-calendar"></i></span>
                                <input type="date" class="form-control" id="attendance_date" value="{{ today }}"
                                    readonly>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card-body p-0">
                    {% if bookings %}
                    <form method="POST" action="{{ url_for('tutor_attendance', activity_id=activity.id) }}">
                        <input type="hidden" name="csrf_token" value="{{ csrf_token() }}" />
                        <input type="hidden" name="date" value="{{ today }}" />

                        <div class="table-responsive">
                            <table class="table table-hover mb-0">
                                <thead class="table-light">
                                    <tr>
                                        <th class="ps-4">Student</th>
                                        <th>Grade</th>
                                        <th>Status</th>
                                        <th>Notes</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                    {% for booking in bookings %}
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="ps-4">
                                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center py-2">
                                                <div class="avatar-circle bg-primary text-white me-3">
                                                    {{ booking.child.name[0] }}
                                                </div>
                                                <div>
                                                    <h6 class="mb-0">{{ booking.child.name }}</h6>
                                                    <small class="text-muted">ID: #{{ booking.child.id }}</small>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="align-middle">
                                            <span class="badge bg-secondary">Grade {{ booking.child.grade }}</span>
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="align-middle">
                                            <div class="btn-group" role="group">
                                                <input type="radio" class="btn-check"
                                                    name="status_{{ booking.child.id }}"
                                                    id="present_{{ booking.child.id }}" value="present" checked>
                                                <label class="btn btn-outline-success"
                                                    for="present_{{ booking.child.id }}">
                                                    <i class="fas fa-check"></i> Present
                                                </label>

                                                <input type="radio" class="btn-check"
                                                    name="status_{{ booking.child.id }}"
                                                    id="late_{{ booking.child.id }}" value="late">
                                                <label class="btn btn-outline-warning"
                                                    for="late_{{ booking.child.id }}">
                                                    <i class="fas fa-clock"></i> Late
                                                </label>

                                                <input type="radio" class="btn-check"
                                                    name="status_{{ booking.child.id }}"
                                                    id="absent_{{ booking.child.id }}" value="absent">
                                                <label class="btn btn-outline-danger"
                                                    for="absent_{{ booking.child.id }}">
                                                    <i class="fas fa-times"></i> Absent
                                                </label>
                                            </div>
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="align-middle">
                                            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="notes_{{ booking.child.id }}"
                                                placeholder="Optional notes...">
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                    {% endfor %}
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>

                        <div class="card-footer bg-white p-4 border-top">
                            <div class="row align-items-center">
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <p class="mb-0 text-muted">
                                        <i class="fas fa-users me-2"></i>
                                        <strong>{{ bookings|length }}</strong> student(s) enrolled
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6 text-end">
                                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary px-5">
                                        <i class="fas fa-save me-2"></i> Save Attendance
                                    </button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </form>

                    {% else %}
                    <div class="text-center py-5">
                        <i class="fas fa-users-slash fa-3x text-muted mb-3"></i>
                        <h5 class="text-muted">No Students Enrolled</h5>
                        <p class="text-muted">There are no confirmed bookings for this activity yet.</p>
                    </div>
                    {% endif %}
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .avatar-circle {
        width: 45px;
        height: 45px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 18px;
    }

    .btn-group label {
        min-width: 90px;
    }

    .table td {
        vertical-align: middle;
    }
</style>
<p>{% endblock %}
```</p></body></html>